{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5f38d9f953","title":"四、破坏党的一元化领导，削弱工宣队的政治作用","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"07fdca6e7c","index":8,"year":1974,"month":4,"day":11,"articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"17cbce4d07","index":7,"year":1974,"month":4,"day":9,"articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"490fb8664a","index":2,"year":1973,"month":12,"day":21,"articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"57d08edd76","index":0,"year":1973,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"95f37145a4","index":5,"year":1974,"month":2,"day":20,"articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"ad24b36e17","index":4,"year":1974,"month":2,"day":19,"articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"af46b66044","index":1,"year":1973,"month":12,"day":1,"articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"bbe9437395","index":3,"year":1974,"month":2,"day":18,"articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"fd6101d79d","index":6,"year":1974,"month":2,"day":22,"articleId":"5f38d9f953"}],"tags":[{"id":"3766d87da7","name":"革命大批判","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"3ab575d9ee","name":"辽宁省教育局大批判组整理","type":"出版方/发行方"},{"id":"ad51b2eae3","name":"批林批孔","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"f8d6ecb146","name":"毛远新","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","name":"“四人帮”死党毛远新破坏教育革命言论摘编（初编）（1976.12）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"img","author":"毛远新，1976.12，反攻倒算材料，辽宁省教育局大批判组整理","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a/1.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a/2.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a/3.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a/4.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a/5.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a/6.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a/7.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a/8.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a/9.png"}],"authors":[{"id":"b7ad58134e","name":"毛远新"}]},"publication_details":{"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a":{"comments":[{"id":"28f79d8337","publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953","index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"辽宁省教育局大批判组整理，一九七六年十二月"}],"contents":[{"id":"64b7d659c3","type":"title","text":"四、破坏党的一元化领导，削弱工宣队的政治作用","index":0,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"8e682899b8","type":"paragraph","text":"名义上是共产党领导的教育局，实际上站在资产阶级知识分子一边。","index":1,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"f7c7344971","type":"signature","text":"（1974年2月22日在鞍山市委常委扩大会上的讲话和插话）","index":2,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"1dfcf31482","type":"paragraph","text":"列宁说过，无政府主义是对机会主义的惩罚，你搞修正主义，他就去搞无政府主义。将来说你教育局是最大的教唆犯，你跳在黄河里也洗不清。","index":3,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"d76afee48b","type":"signature","text":"（1974年2月20日在鞍山市委常委扩大会上的讲话）","index":4,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"a8a6a67cfe","type":"paragraph","text":"那几个党员，都是从知识分子里提拔的，不代表工人阶级就代表资产阶级。他们能代表共产党，工宣队就不能代表共产党？","index":5,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"5e79b3aa51","type":"signature","text":"（同上）","index":6,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"804cc67c22","type":"paragraph","text":"工宣队要在党的领导下，这完全正确，但是不是在党支部领导下，看你是什么路线。","index":7,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"6cffc63e36","type":"signature","text":"（同上）","index":8,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"66a3beb8d3","type":"paragraph","text":"和知识分子斗我们不怕，我们怕的是教育部门共产党的组织，党的领导同志，屁股坐在知识分子那边，替资产阶级知识分子说话。","index":9,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"05eceed635","type":"signature","text":"（同上）","index":10,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"8e95390076","type":"paragraph","text":"我们一些管教育的党的干部，是不是忘记了自己是共产党员，无产阶级的先锋队的一个成员，在教育阵地上不支持工人阶级，反而一屁股坐在资产阶级知识分子一边，反对工人阶级。请问，你这个共产党员，无产阶级先锋队的称号配不配？","index":11,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"f824766c71","type":"signature","text":"（1974年4月11日在省教育战线工宣队工作会议上的讲话）","index":12,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"ab0cd3d6b0","type":"paragraph","text":"从大学组织工作考虑，长期搞学校工作的人，再搞学校工作不一定合适，要另找外行，如县委书记、厂党委书记来交流一下，把厂党委书记换一换，学校就是要外行来管，一内行就变过去了。","index":13,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"02b086b8e6","type":"signature","text":"（1973年12月1日在高等院校工代表座谈会上的插话）","index":14,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"cbe8469156","type":"paragraph","text":"要你党支部干什么？你这个党支部是不是共产党的党支部还值得怀疑！","index":15,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"faceb5c27b","type":"signature","text":"（1974年2月18日在鞍山市四中座谈会上的讲话）","index":16,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"ea83f89844","type":"paragraph","text":"你党支部是带头复辟，支持教员搞资本主义。","index":17,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"d76b6c876e","type":"signature","text":"（同上）","index":18,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"b7454b8976","type":"paragraph","text":"学校党组织不起作用，不起好的作用，最讨厌，成天为资产阶级知识分子服务。……向资产阶级投降。","index":19,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"e78effec05","type":"signature","text":"（1973年12月1日在高等院校工代表座谈会上的插话）","index":20,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"00e0cac4e6","type":"paragraph","text":"如果说（青少年犯罪）一段时间里多了些，我说正是学校里某些领导干部和教员一个是公开怠工，一个是坚持资产阶级偏见造成的。","index":21,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"b244e875a4","type":"signature","text":"（1974年4月9日在省教育战线工宣队工作会议上对会议领导小组和各市、地负责同志的讲话）","index":22,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"db33e0188d","type":"paragraph","text":"你们反而却训练学生犯罪，如果说是教唆犯，你们学校是最大的教唆犯。","index":23,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"a56c3d52f9","type":"paragraph","text":"什么争夺青少年，屁话！是替资产阶级争夺青少年。","index":24,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"b45e103d50","type":"signature","text":"（1974年2月19日在鞍山四十三中座谈会上的讲话）","index":25,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"5fc1465e43","type":"paragraph","text":"你们学校还争论党内有没有阶级斗争，还争论什么？！×××是共产党员吗？我看是国民党，根本不够共产党员，不过打着共产党的招牌，在这里搞资产阶级专政。","index":26,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"bf230fad5b","type":"signature","text":"（1974年2月18日在鞍山四中的讲话）","index":27,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"d771096b4e","type":"paragraph","text":"这次正好毛主席亲自发动和领导了批林批孔运动，我们就是要把修正主义复辟打下去，要求老师丢掉过去那套吧，和学生、家长一块斗争。你不斗，他就斗你，你对他那么客气，他对你毫不客气，有后台，区里就有，市文教部门本身就有问题，路线错了，下面必然产生这些问题，这个问题不单单是区里的，上边这样做，下面必然出问题。","index":28,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"6d68b888af","type":"signature","text":"（1974年2月18日在鞍山市四中座谈会上的讲话）","index":29,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"a27639254d","type":"paragraph","text":"你（指工宣队）要去斗，不斗下一次就要骑在你脖子上拉屎，…要打进攻仗，不要光是防守。","index":30,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"2f0fa7f162","type":"signature","text":"（1973年12月1日在高等院校工代表座谈会上的插话）","index":31,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"aebf9c766f","type":"paragraph","text":"所以开这个会，不光是解剖教育战线，对其他战线也有好处。今天开这个会，请些青年同志来讲，恐怕有些话不大好讲，刺耳一些，但听了有好处。今天给会议吹进点“氧气”进来了，给你们市委吹了“氧气”。","index":32,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"d6c34456a0","type":"signature","text":"（1974年2月20日在鞍山市委常委扩大会上的讲话）","index":33,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"80372c0961","type":"paragraph","text":"要求工宣队的同志、各级教育部门，……敢于向资产阶级意识形态、资产阶级知识分子的错误针锋相对地斗争。批判资产阶级思想，而且更重要的是敢于向各级党委，包括省委在内，各级文教部门的错误路线进行坚决的斗争。","index":34,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"81ef4286a3","type":"signature","text":"（1974年4月11日在省教育战线工宣队工作会议上的讲话）","index":35,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"8853a4ca61","type":"paragraph","text":"中学留下三、五个（指工宣队）就行了，小学可以留三个，农村可以不留（指贫宣队）。","index":36,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"},{"id":"651010f442","type":"signature","text":"（1973年在省工宣队会议上的讲话）","index":37,"publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953"}],"page":{"id":"d5900ad3d3","publicationId":"93482dc4-edc3-4ce3-a6d2-960ec210656a","articleId":"5f38d9f953","start":7,"end":9}}}},"__N_SSG":true}